OL,3,CPassenger denied boarding her flight
OL,4,Cbecause of her epilepsy
OL,6,FA woman has spoken of her
OL,7,Fembarrassment and frustration after
OL,8,Fbeing turned away from boarding a
OL,9,FLoganair flight to Jersey at the last
OL,10,Fminute due to her epilepsy.
OL,12,FEmily Bownes had declared her
OL,13,Fcondition on Loganair's website when
OL,14,Fbooking the flight from Southampton,
OL,15,Fwhere she is studying to become a
OL,16,Fnurse.
OL,18,FThe booking form asks passengers to
OL,19,Fdeclare whether they have any
OL,20,Fdisabilities, with a checkbox listing
OL,21,Fadditional requirements.
