OL,3,CPassenger denied boarding her flight
OL,4,Cbecause of her epilepsy
OL,6,FThe 25-year-old said she checked the
OL,7,F'non-visible disability' box, which
OL,8,Fthe airline lists as 'passenger has a
OL,9,Fnon-visible disability and may require
OL,10,Fsome extra assistance'.
OL,12,F"I felt like this was the morally
OL,13,Fright thing to do", she told ITV News.
OL,15,FIn the days before her scheduled
OL,16,Fflight, Ms Bownes was contacted by a
OL,17,Frepresentative from the Scottish
OL,18,Fairline to discuss her condition and
OL,19,Fneeds as an epileptic traveller.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
