OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F388A1765371361
OL,3,CPassenger denied boarding her flight
OL,4,Cbecause of her epilepsy
OL,6,F"The lady on the phone asked about my
OL,7,Fepilepsy and if I needed any
OL,8,Fassistance getting on or off the
OL,9,Fplane, when my last seizure was, and
OL,10,Fhow often these happen."
OL,12,FMs Bownes also explained that she
OL,13,Fcarries rescue medicine with her and
OL,14,Fis capable of administering the
OL,15,Fmedication herself most of the time.
OL,17,FShe was informed that her medical
OL,18,Fnotes had been documented so the cabin
OL,19,Fcrew would be aware of her condition.
