OL,3,CPassenger denied boarding her flight
OL,4,Cbecause of her epilepsy
OL,6,F"It was humiliating to be told this at
OL,7,Fthe boarding gate - in front of other
OL,8,Fpassengers, while everyone was looking
OL,9,Fat me," Ms Bownes told ITV News. "It
OL,10,Flooked like I'd done something wrong."
OL,12,FAlthough Swissport made an
OL,13,Fannouncement asking if there were any
OL,14,Fmedical professionals on board, they
OL,15,Fwere unable to find anyone suitable,
OL,16,Fmeaning Ms Bownes was unable to fly
OL,17,Fthat day.
