OL,3,CPassenger denied boarding her flight
OL,4,Cbecause of her epilepsy
OL,6,FThe situation has left Ms Bownes
OL,7,Fquestioning the purpose of the initial
OL,8,Fphone call with Loganair: "As I wasn't
OL,9,Ftold I need anything, such as a 'fit
OL,10,Fto fly letter', I didn't think there
OL,11,Fwould be any issues."
OL,13,FMs Bownes admits epilepsy is a
OL,14,F"complex" condition, but points out
OL,15,Fthat her seizures can be treated with
OL,16,F"basic first aid" procedures.
OL,18,FShe said she had never experienced
OL,19,Fthis issue before with another airline.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
