OL,3,CPassenger denied boarding her flight
OL,4,Cbecause of her epilepsy
OL,6,FIn the days following the incident, Ms
OL,7,FBownes explained she has been left
OL,8,Fwith heightened anxiety, something
OL,9,Fwhich she explained to ITV News can
OL,10,F"bring on" her seizures.
OL,12,FMs Bownes claimed that she had a
OL,13,Fseizure when she eventually returned
OL,14,Fto Jersey due to the "stress and
OL,15,Femotion" caused by the incident.
OL,17,F"On the flight the following day, I
OL,18,Fwasn't questioned at all about my
OL,19,Fepilepsy. It was like nothing had
OL,20,Fhappened".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
