OL,4,Cbecause of her epilepsy
OL,6,FLoganair offered to pay for Ms Bownes'
OL,7,Ftaxi to and from the airport and a
OL,8,Fhotel for the extra night she had to
OL,9,Fstay in Southampton until her next
OL,10,Fflight the following day.
OL,12,FLoganair has provided a statement to
OL,13,FITV News, which reads: "We treat the
OL,14,Fmedical circumstances of our customers
OL,15,Fvery seriously, and as such, we take
OL,16,Fevery precaution necessary to ensure
OL,17,Fcustomers with additional requirements
OL,18,Fare fully supported.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
