OL,3,CPassenger denied boarding her flight
OL,4,Cbecause of her epilepsy
OL,6,F"Loganair is dedicated to its
OL,7,Fcustomers, and safety will always be
OL,8,Four top priority. Thankfully, our team
OL,9,Fworked hard to ensure the customer was
OL,10,Fable to travel on the next available
OL,11,Fflight.
OL,13,F"We thank the customer for their
OL,14,Fpatience and understanding during this
OL,15,Ftime and apologise for any
OL,16,Finconvenience caused to her journey."
OL,18,FThe Jersey to Southampton route was
OL,19,Fformerly run by Blue Islands before it
OL,20,Fcollapsed last month.
